========
Abstract
========
docsimplepuj is a small package for the consistent formatting of simple documents (class syllabus, reports, class assignments, etc.) for the Pontificia Universidad Javeriana.

This is not an official package from the University, but does try its best to adhere to the institutional image manual from the University.

=====
Usage
=====
Add \usepackage{docsimplepuj} to your tex file and that's it. See the ./ejemplos folder for a quick rundown of what can be done with this package.

This package has been tested with the article class document.

